(146, '10147', '2010-02-10', 'February 10, 2010Release # 10-136 Firm\'s Recall Hotline: (888) 791-8166CPSC Recall Hotline: (800) 638-2772CPSC Media Contact: (301) 504-7908HC Media Contact: (613) 957-2983 Tiny Love Recalls Wind Chime Toys Due to Puncture and Laceration Hazards WASHINGTON, D.C. - The U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission and Health Canada, in cooperation with the firm named below, today announced a voluntary recall of the following consumer product. Consumers should stop using recalled products immediately unless otherwise instructed. It is illegal to resell or attempt to resell a recalled consumer product. Name of Product: Wind Chime Toys Units: About 600,000 in the United States and 200,000 in Canada Distributor: Tiny Love Inc., of New York, N.Y. and the Maya Group Inc., of Huntington Beach, Calif. Hazard: The wind chime toy can be pulled apart exposing sharp metal rods, posing puncture and laceration hazards to the baby. Incidents-Injuries: The firm has received five reports of babies pulling apart the wind chimes exposing the sharp metal rods, including a report of a minor injury to a 24-month-old baby who punctured his cheek with the rods. Description: This recall involves wind chime toys sold separately, with the Gymini Kick and Play Activity Gym and Tiny Smarts Gift Sets. The toy produces the sound of a wind chime. \"Tiny Love\" is printed on a tag on the toy. The following names and item numbers are included in this recall: Note: clicking on some of the images below will allow you to view a larger version. Picture Name Item Number Baby Wind Chime # 493 Baby Wind Chime - Ocean # 593 Tiny Smarts - Baby Bunny # 512 Wind Chime - Duck*The Wind Chime - Duck is soldwith the Gymini Kick and PlayActivity Gym. Only the WindChime is affected by this Recall <span style=\"font-size: x-smfont-size: x-small;\"># 512 Wind Chime - Duck*The Wind Chime - Duck se vendecon el Gymini Kick and PlayActivity Gym. Este retiro del.mercado afecta solo a la campanita. # 811 Wind Chime - Louie # 516 Wind Chime - Ella # 517 Tiny Smarts Gift Set*El único producto afectadopor este retiro del mercadoes Bunny Wind Chime. # 539 Las campanitas que se venden con otros Tiny Love Activity Gyms no están incluidas en este retiro del mercado. En venta en: Tiendas Toys R Us, Walmart, Target, Buy Buy Baby y TJ Maxx de todo el país desde febrero de 2002 hasta febrero de 2010 por aproximadamente $8 separadamente, us$22 por los Tiny Smarts Gift Sets y $70 con el Gymini Kick and Play Activity Gym. Fabricado en: China Remedio: Los consumidores deben quitarle a los bebés inmediatamente las campanitas retiradas del mercado y ponerse en contacto con Tiny Love para recibir un juguete de reemplazo gratuito. Contacto para consumidores: Para mayor información, llame gratis a Tiny Love al (888) 791-8166 entre las 8 a.m. y las 5 p.m. hora del Este de lunes a viernes, o visite el sitio web de la firma en www.tinylove.com Nota: El comunicado de prensa de Health Canada está disponible en http:--cpsr-rspc.hc-sc.gc.ca-PR-RP-recall-retrait-eng.jsp?re_id=974 English Versionall;\"># 811 Wind Chime - Louie # 516 Wind Chime - Ella # 517 Tiny Smarts Gift Set*Bunny Wind Chime is the onlyproduct affected by this Recall. # 539 Wind chimes sold with other Tiny Love Activity Gyms are not included in this recall. Sold at: Toys R Us, Walmart, Target, Buy Buy Baby and TJ Maxx stores nationwide from February 2002 through February 2010 for about $8 separately, $22 for the Tiny Smarts Gift Sets and $70 with the Gymini Kick and Play Activity Gym. Manufactured in: China Remedy: Consumers should immediately take the recalled wind chimes from babies and contact Tiny Love to receive a free replacement toy. Consumer Contact: For additional information, contact Tiny Love toll-free at (888) 791-8166 between 8 a.m. and 5 p.m. ET Monday through Friday, or visit the firm\'s Web site at www.tinylove.com Note: Health Canada\'s press release is available at http:--cpsr-rspc.hc-sc.gc.ca-PR-RP-recall-retrait-eng.jsp?re_id=97', 'Tiny Love Recalls Wind Chime Toys Due to Puncture and Laceration Hazards', '2014-10-23', 'Tiny Love Baby Wind Chime, Wind Chime - Ocean; Tiny Smarts - Baby Bunny Wind Chime Toys', 'https:--www.cpsc.gov-Recalls-2010-Tiny-Love-Recalls-Wind-Chime-Toys-Due-to-Puncture-and-Laceration-Hazards'),
