een 8 a.m. and 4:30 p.m. ET Monday through Friday, or visit the firm\'s web site at www.djgusa.com', 'CPSC, Dorel Juvenile Group Announce Recall of Cosco Playpens', '2014-05-23', 'Cosco Okie Dokie playpen', 'https:--www.cpsc.gov-Recalls-2002-CPSC-Dorel-Juvenile-Group-Announce-Recall-of-Cosco-Playpens'),
