h Traveler Ltd. Announce Recall of Child Backpack Carriers', '2014-05-23', 'Tough Traveler Filly Child Backpack Carriers', 'https:--www.cpsc.gov-Recalls-2002-CPSC-Tough-Traveler-Ltd-Announce-Recall-of-Child-Backpack-Carriers'),
